Audi A6 th h th hai c sn xut da trn khung gm Volkswagen Group C5 vi chiu di c s khng i so vi th h u tin (2,760 mm).

Cc la chn v ng c a dng hn th h trc bao gm: ng c xng 1.8L I4 20 van, 2.0L I4 20 van, 2.4L V6 30 van, 2.8L V6 30 van, 3.0L V6 30 van, 4.2L V8 40 van; ng c tng p 1.8L I4 20 van Turbo, 2.7L V6 30 van Turbo; ng c diesel tng p phun nhin liu trc tip 1.9L I4 8 van TDI, 2.5L V6 24 van TDI.

Hp s c trang b bao gm hp s tay 5 cp, 6 cp; hp s t ng bin thin lin tc CVT (Continuously Variable Transmission) 5 cp multitronic v hp s t ng 5 cp tiptronic.
